0C12076E.Line13.A9B7A: Could you see if he’s there? He has a tattoo on his neck. A seafarer’s spear.

2AF01661.Line7.A9B7A: I heard his vessel met the rocks beyond Stormbreak Cove. Tore it to pieces.

5C48333B.VoiceDir13.A9B7A: Steady. Imploring player to help him.

721D8DEC.Line11.A9B7A: He’s like a brother. It’s not right.

90FB9CDF.Line5.A9B7A: He was my best mate. Took to the sea a fortnight ago and hasn’t returned.

C4E48FE3.Line9.A9B7A: I’d give the coast a look myself, but I...I can’t see him like that. Welled up with water, fit to burst.
